第二届  逐鹿雷霆  楚国  楚魂V随风随行 http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMzI5MTA0NjA=.html?f=2583081 {{Wayback|url=http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMzI5MTA0NjA=.html?f=2583081 |date=20191202135526 }}
